{#- LLM-facing text is English-only: Cyrillic uses roughly 2–3× more tokens per word.
    This Jinja comment is stripped and never sent to the model.
-#}

{#- Canonical incoming mail text for ``--- user message ---``, ``original_question``, and plan LLM.
    Variables: ``incoming`` — stdlib ``EmailMessage``. No References; plain/html body via ``get_body``.
    Operator-editable; fields extracted here, not in Python. -#}
From: {{ incoming.get('From', '') }}
To: {{ incoming.get('To', '') }}
Subject: {{ incoming.get('Subject', '') }}
Message-ID: {{ incoming.get('Message-ID', '') }}
In-Reply-To: {{ incoming.get('In-Reply-To', '') }}

{% set part = incoming.get_body(preferencelist=('plain', 'html')) %}
{% if part %}
{{ part.get_content() }}
{% endif %}
